    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "We haven't yet decided if we're going to implement this @hrik2001, we'd like to get feedback instead.\r\n\r\nAlthough `Ownable2Step` seems like a good option to avoid accidental mistakes, we're discussing that `TransparentUpgradeableProxy` should deploy its own `ProxyAdmin`, therefore, its bytecode size might be a concern. A gas cost analysis would help to answer whether this is a good addition or not.",
